name: LogChain
description: LogChain is a decentralized provenance application that tracks the ownership and movement of a product or asset through its life cycle. It helps to authenticate the product and prevent any sale of counterfeit goods.

name: fitQuest
description: FitQuest solves the problem of inconsistency in fitness and wellness habits by providing users with a platform that encourages and rewards them for forming good fitness habits and staying committed to their goals.
